            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "滬深A股早市表現牛皮 龍蟠科技顯著回吐",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市連升兩日後，今早轉為牛皮格局，個別近日急升的股份如龍蟠科技(02465)A股(603906.SH)更顯著回吐。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：龍蟠科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241021_FI_source-web_Lopal.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：龍蟠科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241021_FI_source-web_Lopal.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：龍蟠科技官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早高開2點後，早市全程便在升5點、報3381點，至最多跌5點、報3371點之間上落，波幅只有10點；滬指中午收報3378點，升2點或 0.08%，半日成交2737.87億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指同樣窄幅橫行，最低見10113點，跌31點，高位10164點也僅升20點，半日高低位相差只有51點；深指中午收報10160點，升16點或0.16%，成交4404.63億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數升2點或0.07%，收報3871點；創業板指數升6點或0.32%，報2031點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">龍蟠科技在港配售H股集資，公司又披露大股東質押了約3000萬股，今早A、H齊跌，A股跌4.67%，報13.28元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股則個別發展，其中保險股再受捧，新華保險(01336)A股(601336.SH)升1.98%，報53.53元；中國人壽(02628)A股(601628.SH)升1.36%，報39.51元；中國平安(02318)A股(601318.SH)也升0.39%，報53.97元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14985833-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1a%e8%82%a1%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e8%a1%a8%e7%8f%be%e7%89%9b%e7%9a%ae-%e9%be%8d%e8%9f%a0%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e9%a1%af%e8%91%97%e5%9b%9e%e5%90%90",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-05 11:40:34",
